{
  "uid": "v12-1-advisor",
  "title": "Grafana 12.1 — Grafana Advisor",
  "description": "The Grafana Advisor (12.1) is a built-in health scanner that flags broken plugins, unhealthy data sources, OIDC misconfig, legacy dashboards, etc. The Plugin Health panel joins the local /api/plugins inventory against the grafana.com marketplace to surface an Update Status (Updated / Not Updated / Not Available) and the plugin's declared Grafana Dependency.",
  "tags": ["grafana-12", "v12.1", "advisor", "v12-demo"],
  "schemaVersion": 40,
  "version": 2,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "1m",
  "time": {"from": "now-15m", "to": "now"},
  "timepicker": {},
  "templating": {"list": [
    {"name": "ds_prom", "type": "datasource", "query": "prometheus", "refresh": 1, "current": {"text": "Prometheus", "value": "prom"}}
  ]},
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1, "type": "text", "title": "",
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "options": {"mode": "markdown", "content": "### Grafana Advisor (12.1)\n\n- **[➡ Open Advisor](/a/grafana-advisor-app)** — runs a fresh health pass and reports plugin / DS / SSO / dashboard issues.\n- Complements `detect-angular-dashboards` (used in `make audit` for the v12 upgrade).\n- The **Plugin Health** panel below joins local `/api/plugins` against the **grafana.com marketplace** so you can see which plugins have an update available before cutover.\n  - 🟢 **Updated** — installed version matches latest on grafana.com\n  - 🔴 **Not Updated** — newer version available on grafana.com\n  - 🟠 **Not Available** — plugin not in the public marketplace (private / internal build)\n- **Grafana Dependency** is read from the marketplace LIST endpoint where present; per-plugin endpoints are not iterated, so internal builds will show `Not Available`."}
    },

    {
      "id": 2, "type": "table",
      "title": "Plugin health (feeds Advisor)",
      "description": "Joins local /api/plugins against grafana.com /api/plugins by plugin_id. Update Status is derived by the calculateField transformation (binary equality between Installed Version and Latest Version Available) and colored via field-override value mappings.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 22, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 6},
      "datasource": {"uid": "-- Mixed --", "type": "datasource"},
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "LOCAL",
          "datasource": {"uid": "grafana-api", "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"},
          "type": "json",
          "source": "url",
          "url": "/api/plugins?embedded=0",
          "url_options": {"method": "GET"},
          "parser": "backend",
          "root_selector": "",
          "format": "table",
          "columns": [
            {"selector": "id",             "text": "plugin_id",         "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "name",           "text": "name",              "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "type",           "text": "plugin_type",       "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "info.version",   "text": "installed_version", "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "signatureType",  "text": "signature",         "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "angularDetected","text": "angular",           "type": "boolean"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "refId": "MARKETPLACE",
          "datasource": {"uid": "grafana-com", "type": "yesoreyeram-infinity-datasource"},
          "type": "json",
          "source": "url",
          "url": "https://grafana.com/api/plugins?orderBy=name&direction=asc",
          "url_options": {"method": "GET"},
          "parser": "backend",
          "root_selector": "items",
          "format": "table",
          "columns": [
            {"selector": "slug",              "text": "plugin_id",          "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "version",           "text": "latest_version",     "type": "string"},
            {"selector": "grafanaDependency", "text": "grafana_dependency", "type": "string"}
          ]
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "joinByField",
          "options": {"byField": "plugin_id", "mode": "outer"}
        },
        {
          "id": "filterFieldsByName",
          "options": {
            "include": {"names": ["plugin_id", "name", "plugin_type", "installed_version", "latest_version", "grafana_dependency", "signature", "angular"]}
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "calculateField",
          "options": {
            "mode": "binary",
            "binary": {
              "left": "installed_version",
              "operator": "==",
              "right": "latest_version"
            },
            "alias": "match",
            "replaceFields": false
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "renameByName": {
              "plugin_id":          "Plugin",
              "name":               "Name",
              "plugin_type":        "Type",
              "installed_version":  "Installed Version",
              "latest_version":     "Latest Version Available",
              "match":              "Update Status",
              "grafana_dependency": "Grafana Dependency",
              "signature":          "Signature",
              "angular":            "Angular"
            },
            "indexByName": {
              "plugin_id": 0, "name": 1, "plugin_type": 2,
              "installed_version": 3, "latest_version": 4,
              "match": 5, "grafana_dependency": 6,
              "signature": 7, "angular": 8
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "cellOptions": {"type": "auto"},
            "filterable": true,
            "align": "auto"
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Update Status"},
            "properties": [
              {"id": "custom.cellOptions", "value": {"type": "color-background", "mode": "basic"}},
              {"id": "mappings", "value": [
                {"type": "value",   "options": {"1":  {"color": "green",  "index": 0, "text": "Updated"}}},
                {"type": "value",   "options": {"0":  {"color": "red",    "index": 1, "text": "Not Updated"}}},
                {"type": "special", "options": {"match": "null+nan", "result": {"color": "orange", "index": 2, "text": "Not Available"}}}
              ]},
              {"id": "custom.width", "value": 140},
              {"id": "noValue", "value": "Not Available"}
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Plugin"},
            "properties": [{"id": "custom.width", "value": 260}]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Name"},
            "properties": [{"id": "custom.width", "value": 200}]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Type"},
            "properties": [{"id": "custom.width", "value": 90}]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Installed Version"},
            "properties": [{"id": "custom.width", "value": 130}]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Latest Version Available"},
            "properties": [{"id": "custom.width", "value": 160}]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Grafana Dependency"},
            "properties": [
              {"id": "custom.width", "value": 180},
              {"id": "noValue", "value": "Not Available"}
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Signature"},
            "properties": [
              {"id": "custom.cellOptions", "value": {"type": "color-background"}},
              {"id": "mappings", "value": [
                {"type": "value", "options": {
                  "grafana":    {"color": "green"},
                  "commercial": {"color": "green"},
                  "community":  {"color": "blue"},
                  "valid":      {"color": "green"},
                  "internal":   {"color": "purple"},
                  "unsigned":   {"color": "red"},
                  "invalid":    {"color": "red"}
                }}
              ]},
              {"id": "custom.width", "value": 110}
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Angular"},
            "properties": [
              {"id": "custom.cellOptions", "value": {"type": "color-background"}},
              {"id": "mappings", "value": [
                {"type": "value", "options": {
                  "true":  {"text": "ANGULAR", "color": "red"},
                  "false": {"text": "React",   "color": "green"}
                }}
              ]},
              {"id": "custom.width", "value": 100}
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true,
        "cellHeight": "sm",
        "footer": {"show": true, "reducer": ["count"], "fields": ["Update Status"]},
        "sortBy": [{"displayName": "Update Status", "desc": false}]
      }
    },

    {
      "id": 3, "type": "stat", "title": "Data sources configured",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 28},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_prom}", "type": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"refId": "A", "expr": "grafana_datasource_request_duration_seconds_count", "instant": true, "format": "table"}],
      "transformations": [{"id": "reduce", "options": {"reducers": ["count"], "labelsToFields": false}}],
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area"},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short"}, "overrides": []}
    },
    {
      "id": 4, "type": "stat", "title": "Plugins with load errors (Advisor: BLOCKER)",
      "gridPos": {"h": 5, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 28},
      "datasource": {"uid": "${ds_prom}", "type": "prometheus"},
      "targets": [{"refId": "A", "expr": "sum(grafana_plugin_load_errors) or on() vector(0)"}],
      "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none"},
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}, {"color": "red", "value": 1}]}, "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}}, "overrides": []}
    }
  ]
}
